logs/

# ----- rendered docs (rebuild with `quarto render docs/`) -----
docs/*.html

# ----- compiled Stan binaries -----
stan/dynamic_irt
stan/*.hpp

# ----- OS -----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ----- readings (licensed PDFs) -----
readings/
